{"tid":1823291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《西部世界》第三季借香港「反送中」風波引發第三次世界大戰","createTime":"2020-01-13T14:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T15:01:16.000Z","uid":28114,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"be226a30b981b40d0e571b86429606bed4cd8ef0","tid":1823291,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T14:30:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2020/1/1578907761_Gf-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2020%2F1%2F1578907761_Gf-1280w.png&h=f2977ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一輯播出時被譽為神劇的《Westworld》(西部世界)，扭橋超現實科幻劇情，比《Black Mirror》(黑鏡)及《Game of Thrones》(權力遊戲)更厲害，講述人物如何借助AI技術來娛樂，可惜AI 機械人開始有自我意識，開始對人類作出反抗。可惜《Westworld》第二季故事枝節繁多，敘事手法亦太複雜，因此未能穩坐「第一美劇寶座」。<br />\n《Westworld》第三季今日宣布將在3月15日播出，但預告片真的震驚香港740萬人，今次《Westworld》的預告片，宣告第一個事件引發點，竟然是香港的反送中修例風波「06.12.19 DIVERGENCE: HONG KONG &ndash; POLITICAL UNREST. WIDE SCALE PROTEST.」引發未來世界大戰。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%e3%80%8a%e8%a5%bf%e9%83%a8%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e3%80%8b%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%89%e5%ad%a3%e5%80%9f%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e3%80%8c%e5%8f%8d%e9%80%81%e4%b8%ad%e3%80%8d%e9%a2%a8%e6%b3%a2%e5%bc%95%e7%99%bc%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%89%e6%ac%a1%e4%b8%96%e7%95%8c%e5%a4%a7%e6%88%b0-203566\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F%25e3%2580%258a%25e8%25a5%25bf%25e9%2583%25a8%25e4%25b8%2596%25e7%2595%258c%25e3%2580%258b%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25b8%2589%25e5%25ad%25a3%25e5%2580%259f%25e9%25a6%2599%25e6%25b8%25af%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%258f%258d%25e9%2580%2581%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e3%2580%258d%25e9%25a2%25a8%25e6%25b3%25a2%25e5%25bc%2595%25e7%2599%25bc%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25b8%2589%25e6%25ac%25a1%25e4%25b8%2596%25e7%2595%258c%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e6%2588%25b0-203566&d=x7%2Fg1uS4a%2BT3911x%2BwLoHODT5CHOggjCyLUuLmpgHOg%3D&h=ad6eb08a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8